songs.title: Flow (I’m The Typa...)
songs.lyrics:
[Hook]
I'm the type of nigga, bring a pick up with a Benz through
You the type of nigga, bring the police and they friends through
I'm the type of nigga, take up four lanes when I slide through
I'm the type of nigga, shoot two bitches when I blast you

[Verse]
Bought my mom a shotgun, she got options when she fire at you
Bought Gigi a paintball gun, he don't need no range practice, boo
Old school green and yellow like the Packers, fool
Hope you don't run up, I'm 'bout to motherfucking whack this fool
I sip that promethazine, I don't even got asthma, dude
I got a bad bitch, I swear this ho got the worst attitude
Bought this bitch a purse and she ain't even showed no gratitude
Cut off my location, fuck that longitude and latitude
Why the fuck you leave the house and you know you ain't had a tool?
My auntie told me to make sure it's you and not me who lose
Got this Asian bitch I took on Oak Street and bough Christian Loubs
Bought my partner'nem a four piece, hope they don't fuck up the loot
My ex bitch got mad at me 'cause she found some condoms used
Told her, "I wasn't doing nothing, you know them other hoes are not you"
Spent twelve hundred on a Yorkie, fed it Benihana's, fool
Diamonds shining, too bright, slant your eyes like marijuana do

[Hook]
I'm the type of nigga, bring a pick up with a Benz through
You the type of nigga, bring the police and they friends through
I'm the type of nigga, take up four lanes when I slide through
I'm the type of nigga, shoot two bitches when I blast you
